:"677f24bc4436bb56ee006ae35781bb307850467f","tid":488272,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T15:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未一齊之前呢？<br />\n一直都係咁？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未一齊梗係唔係啦<br />\n一齊左之後先係<br />\n我地用左好多時間了解對方<br />\n半年左右先一齊"},{"pid":"61112188da2b28640a775ff65d24958768e03373","tid":488272,"uid":58970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T15:28:57.000Z","msg":"我同ex六年都分左啦<br />\n以前根本互相呃對方呃自己過得開心<br />\n一到左兩個人關係既考驗 即刻見真章<br />\n而家分左一個月傷過痛過反而有少少慶幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你真係因爲唔捨得先唔分<br />\n就分左佢擺啦<br />\n唔好互相耽誤對方啦<br />\n最多咪傷心一兩個月<br />\n好過又拖下拖下令大家唔開心更耐"},{"pid":"10ddf4be1993c6cf92b36d2cb98cc4484992f3e1","tid":488272,"uid":74088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T15:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c027df6ea0f8aca3c521c847c9468fc29ae2e134","tid":488272,"uid":74088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T15:35:17.000Z","msg":"Btw 尼你老"}]}